  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.ITriangulatable' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.ITriangulatable' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Common_Decomposition_CDT_ITriangulatable'>Interface ITriangulatable    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Common/Decomposition/CDT/ITriangulatable.cs#L38'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.html'>Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.ITriangulatable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The triangulatable interface</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>internal interface ITriangulatable</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Properties</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.ITriangulatable.GetPoints' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.ITriangulatable.GetPoints' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Common_Decomposition_CDT_ITriangulatable_GetPoints'>GetPoints    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Common/Decomposition/CDT/ITriangulatable.cs#L43'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.ITriangulatable.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the value of the points</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>IList&lt;TriangulationPoint&gt; GetPoints { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.ilist-1'>IList</a>&lt;<a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Common.Decomposition.CDT.TriangulationPoint.html'>TriangulationPoint</